snippet.title: Goomba's Easter Egg Hunt - Easter Special! [Release Trailer]
snippet.description:
For more fangames, subscribe to this channel!
https://www.youtube.com/c/KazeEmanuar?sub_confirmation=1

This mod features:
- 0 new stars
- 20 new colourful easter eggs
- Goomba 
- 8 custom levels


Download:
https://mega.nz/#!mSQRhC4Z!sOCtCyjMd_TkDGNiI17Kfss9eSb7EdtqMy_NsLH6LpQ

Credits:
Kaze - coding&drawing levels&everything else
https://www.youtube.com/user/DobieMeltfire - music
https://www.youtube.com/user/UED - modelrips
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVGuVoCiRE01CqOW0YvkT7w - drawing levels
https://www.youtube.com/user/pidi64 - drawing levels
https://www.youtube.com/user/BroDute - drawing levels
https://www.youtube.com/user/iAmManuze - graphics

This mod obviously can't match the major mod im working on quality wise and this whole thing took less effort than a single level in my major project. I simply felt like making a sequel to the thwomp mod from 2 years ago. Don't take this mod too serious.

Goomba can't use any of the advanced jumps. He can't use any punches or dives. You won't be warped out of a level when collecting an easteregg and also won't be able to safe after getting a star. How many eggs can you collect before game overing?

song used:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HtZXAJ8AMUs
